    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "Department of Justice",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "Washington, D. C.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Dear Mr. Hoover:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "It is requested that this letter be returned to the above",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "address and no record of it kept in FBI files.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "If is it true that the Soviet leaders intend to use the",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "flying disk in an attempt to confuse and terrify the American",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "people, why should we not state to the United Nations that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "we believe this condition to exist and further request per-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "mission from United Nations to fly American printed statements",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "into the USSR in the interests of peace and better understanding",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "between the two nations? To prevent the belief that such a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "method would be used, be either nation, to carry bombs rather",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "than paper, it should be pointed out that it is not necessary",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "to employ airplanes for the purpose insofar as actually flying",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "over enemy territory is concerned. There are several possible",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "means of placing information at the disposal of citizens of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "either country via air; I mention small balloons incapable of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "carrying more than a few pounds or pinned, cardboard disks",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "capable of drifting on wind currents for great distances after",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "release from several miles height. (I reserve the right to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "claim patent rights to the latter \"flying newspaper\".)",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "Inasmuch as we have been told that the Communist Party is a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "very small minority in the USSR, it is impossible to prevent",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "information, printed, from reaching many good people there if",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "flown in by the millions. Of course there would be a penalty",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "in Russia for reading them if caught, but curiosity being",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "curiosity, many would be read and remembered. And no one",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "really believes that children could be prevented from picking",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "up objects floating in from another country.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "INDEXED - 36 RECORDED - 36 62-83994-201",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "Shall freedom of the press be defended in some countries at",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "cost in lives, yet denied across nations, they better being",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "contrary to United Nations principles?",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "Yours sincerely,",
